            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>
                        <persName>Ildebrandus</persName> filius <persName>b.m.
                            Tecti</persName> et <persName>Lieta</persName> genitrix eius et
                        relicta qd. suprascripti Tecti et filia <persName>b.m.
                            Oppiti</persName> ricevuto a nome di <persName key="#Abbots"
                            >Brunus</persName> in Christi nomine <rs key="#Abbots">abbas</rs> de <rs
                            key="#Churches">ecclesia</rs> et <rs key="#Monasteries">monasterii</rs>
                        <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/71" key="#Churches #Monasteries">Sancti
                            Pontiani</orgName> (…) meritum da <persName key="#Judge">Iohannes <rs
                                key="#Judge">iudex</rs></persName> pro pendo uno ex auro pro solidis
                        duocemtum pro persona tua qui supra Brunus abbati (…) promettono di non
                        contestare o sottrarre de tertia portione ex integra et de alia tertia
                        portione ex integra due portiones ex imtegre de una <rs
                            key="#Casae/cassinae_massaricie">cassina et re massaricia</rs> que esse
                        videtur in loco et finibus <placeName
                            key="#Casae/cassinae_massaricie #Wine #Fiscal_property #Mention #Emperor/king"
                            ref="#places/36">Saltucclo</placeName>, ubi dicitur <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Wine #Fiscal_property #Mention #Emperor/king"
                                ><placeName ref="#places/36">Vinea Regis</placeName></rs>, que recta
                        et laborata esse videtur per *** massarium quas tibi per <rs key="#Venditio"
                            >cartulam</rs> scripta ex manibus <persName key="#Notary">Conradi <rs
                                key="#Notary">notarii</rs></persName> domini imperatoris ex
                        comparatione obvenit a nobis ipsis. Pena: argentum obtimum libras viginti.
                        (…) Actum <placeName ref="#places/4">Luca</placeName>. SM Ildebrandi
                        et Liete. SM <persName>Alberti</persName> filii <persName>b.m.
                            Teudegrimi iudicis</persName>. SM <persName>Henrichi</persName>
                        filii b.m. <persName>Iohannis iudicis</persName>. SM <persName
                            >Mucciani</persName> filii <persName>b.m. Barocci</persName>.
                        Scrive: <persName key="#Notary">Conradus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> domini imperatoris </ab>
